::Kluster::

Kluster looks up at the two other bots as they enter. He is about to answer 
when the scanners beep.

"Bot aproaching."

Kluster points to a screen, displaying the exterior of the ship. "That," he 
says, looking at the strange centaur creature.

"Come with me, let's check it out," he says, walking out of the bridge.
